{"@context":"http://iiif.io/api/presentation/3/context.json","id":"https://digbmc.github.io/pta-manifests/phan/phan-12745/manifest.json","type":"Manifest","label":{"none":["PHAN-12745"]},"metadata":[{"label":{"none":["Timestamp"]},"value":{"none":["1:27:45"]}},{"label":{"none":["Film"]},"value":{"none":["Phantom Thread"]}},{"label":{"none":["Distance"]},"value":{"none":["close-up"]}},{"label":{"none":["Angle"]},"value":{"none":["high"]}},{"label":{"none":["Location"]},"value":{"none":["interior"]}},{"label":{"none":["Movement"]},"value":{"none":["fixed"]}}],"summary":{"none":["fingers hold onto upside down dress label"]},"thumbnail":[{"id":"https://digitalscholarship.brynmawr.edu/pta/phan/phan-12745/tiles/full/300,169/0/default.jpg","type":"Image","format":"image/jpeg","height":169,"width":300}],"homepage":[{"id":"PHAN-12745","type":"Text","format":"text/html","label":{"none":["Object homepage"]}}],"items":[{"id":"https://digitalscholarship.brynmawr.edu/pta/phan/phan-12745/canvas/1","type":"Canvas","height":1080,"width":1920,"label":{"none":["PHAN-12745"]},"thumbnail":[{"id":"https://digitalscholarship.brynmawr.edu/pta/phan/phan-12745/tiles/full/300,169/0/default.jpg","type":"Image","format":"image/jpeg","height":169,"width":300}],"items":[{"id":"https://digitalscholarship.brynmawr.edu/pta/phan/phan-12745/canvas/1/annopage-1","type":"AnnotationPage","items":[{"id":"https://digitalscholarship.brynmawr.edu/pta/phan/phan-12745/canvas/1/annopage-1/anno-1","type":"Annotation","motivation":"painting","target":"https://digitalscholarship.brynmawr.edu/pta/phan/phan-12745/canvas/1","body":{"id":"https://digitalscholarship.brynmawr.edu/pta/phan/phan-12745/tiles/full/1920,1080/0/default.jpg","type":"Image","format":"image/jpeg","height":1080,"width":1920,"service":[{"id":"https://digitalscholarship.brynmawr.edu/pta/phan/phan-12745/tiles","type":"ImageService3","profile":"http://iiif.io/api/image/3/level0.json"}]}}]}],"annotations":[{"id":"https://digitalscholarship.brynmawr.edu/pta/phan/phan-12745/canvas/1/page/p1","type":"AnnotationPage","items":[{"id":"https://digitalscholarship.brynmawr.edu/pta/phan/phan-12745/canvas/1/ea085265-cab4-484e-971a-088c2a644295","type":"Annotation","motivation":"commenting","body":[{"created":"2026-06-30T18:06:49.845Z","creator":"lucia","purpose":"commenting","type":"TextualBody","format":"text/html","value":"<p>Alma discovers that Reynolds has placed one of his hidden messages—a phantom thread—in the Princess’s wedding dress: “never cursed.” This phrase refers to what Reynolds told Alma about dress superstitions on their first date. It is in essence a wish for a happy marriage. PTA has noted that in screenings he attended, he enjoyed seeing how audience members would turn their heads to make sense of the message “<a target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer noopener\" class=\"Hyperlink SCXW114429219 BCX2\" href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=f3It380DGqk\"><u>PHANTOM THREAD - AUDIO - Paul Thomas Anderson in conversation with Alan Parker</u></a>”).&nbsp;</p>"}],"target":{"type":"SpecificResource","source":"https://digitalscholarship.brynmawr.edu/pta/phan/phan-12745/canvas/1","selector":{"type":"FragmentSelector","conformsTo":"http://www.w3.org/TR/media-frags/","value":"xywh=pixel:868.8311688311684,260.2597402597406,578.9610389610388,787.7922077922077"}}},{"id":"https://digitalscholarship.brynmawr.edu/pta/phan/phan-12745/canvas/1/8511d4db-c5ac-4c0a-b677-f30fc4388457","type":"Annotation","motivation":"commenting","body":[{"created":"2026-06-30T18:07:20.879Z","creator":"lucia","purpose":"commenting","type":"TextualBody","format":"text/html","value":"<p>Alma seeing the note that the dress is “never cursed” is perhaps a nod to Reynolds’s incoming proposal. Alma, who gets married after having worked on a wedding dress, escapes the curse through Reynolds.&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;</p>"}],"target":{"type":"SpecificResource","source":"https://digitalscholarship.brynmawr.edu/pta/phan/phan-12745/canvas/1","selector":{"type":"FragmentSelector","conformsTo":"http://www.w3.org/TR/media-frags/","value":"xywh=pixel:59.2207792207774,81.03896103896102,320.25974025974034,174.54545454545453"}}}]}]}]}